info.name: Classic Mawa Cake - 300grams
info.description: This cake is a popular Indian dessert that is known for its rich and flavorful taste. It is a moist and indulgent delicacy made with a combination of mawa, which is a thickened milk solids used in Indian sweets, and other key ingredients. The cake has a dense yet soft texture that melts in your mouth, making it a delightful treat for your taste buds. [4 Servings, Protein(g)-24, Carbs(g)-152, Total fibre (g)-3, Energy(kcal)-1486]

info.name: Oreo Truffle cake
info.description: This Cake is a delightful and indulgent dessert that combines the beloved flavor of Oreo cookies with a creamy, luscious texture. It's a treat that's sure to please Oreo enthusiasts and dessert lovers alike.

info.name: Nutty Truffle Cake
info.description: It is a delectable dessert that combines the rich flavors of chocolate and nuts to create a delightful and indulgent treat, offering a perfect balance of sweetness, creaminess, and nuttiness. This cake is sure to please those who appreciate the delightful combination of chocolate and nuts in a dessert.

info.name: Choco Caramel Crunch Cake
info.description: Indulge in a symphony of flavors with our Choco Caramel Crunch—a delectable fusion of rich chocolate, gooey caramel, and a satisfying crunch that will delight your taste buds. Each bite is a harmonious dance of textures and tastes, creating a moment of pure indulgence.

info.name: Opulent Butterscotch Bliss Cake
info.description: This cake is a delicious dessert that features the rich and distinct flavor of butterscotch. It's a type of cake that incorporates butterscotch flavor into various components, creating a delightful treat for those who enjoy the unique combination, best cake for celebrations.
